If you want to become a first-class manager⸺

264
00:23:03,423 --> 00:23:06,259
It's no good just writing seriously

265
00:23:06,343 --> 00:23:07,928
things that aren't interesting

266
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:09,846
Sorry

267
00:23:09,930 --> 00:23:12,307
(Kyoko) Ah, uh, okay.

268
00:23:12,974 --> 00:23:16,728
I think it was good that Reo-kun's sincere feelings were conveyed.

269
00:23:17,771 --> 00:23:23,110
But what I want to say is that that's not enough.

270
00:23:28,698 --> 00:23:31,952
I want you to enjoy this more.

271
00:23:32,035 --> 00:23:34,496
I want you to be excited.

272
00:23:34,579 --> 00:23:37,040
It's not a formal thing.

273
00:23:38,959 --> 00:23:40,252
Hehe...

274
00:23:41,670 --> 00:23:42,754
You

275
00:23:42,838 --> 00:23:46,091
It seems like you don't know much about the world yet.

276
00:23:50,178 --> 00:23:52,681
If you want to become a first-class manager⸺

277
00:23:52,764 --> 00:23:57,519
First of all, please make me excited

278
00:23:58,603 --> 00:24:00,313
The story starts from that

279
00:24:01,731 --> 00:24:02,941
Woohoo...

280
00:24:10,157 --> 00:24:13,368
Oh, I'm about to leave, please turn the car around.

281
00:24:13,451 --> 00:24:14,911
(Fuyu) I was smart.

282
00:24:14,995 --> 00:24:16,037
What about Kyoko?

283
00:24:16,121 --> 00:24:18,331
(Fuyu) You haven't gone home yet.

284
00:24:18,415 --> 00:24:21,793
What are you doing? Until this time

285
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:34,806
(shutter sound)

286
00:24:40,604 --> 00:24:43,690
(Masayuki) But why does it take this long?

287
00:24:43,773 --> 00:24:48,445
Miyabi is so neglected that she doesn't realize how much of a mother she is.

288
00:24:48,528 --> 00:24:50,864
(Erika) About your father-in-law and your future business plans⸺

289
00:24:50,947 --> 00:24:52,490
I'm so excited

290
00:24:52,574 --> 00:24:55,493
You can't just cut it off from me, right?

291
00:24:56,161 --> 00:25:00,790
I also want to quickly become a great president like Masayuki-san.

292
00:25:02,834 --> 00:25:05,462
Let's do it together with Interfashion.

293
00:25:05,545 --> 00:25:07,714
I'm the president of Ise Bussan.

294
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:13,845
sorry

295
00:25:14,679 --> 00:25:18,683
The world is now paying attention to the work I'm involved in.

296
00:25:18,767 --> 00:25:19,809
You see?

297
00:25:21,102 --> 00:25:22,354
Yeah

298
00:25:22,437 --> 00:25:25,982
The weight of responsibility is different from other managers.

299
00:25:26,066 --> 00:25:28,109
It's not enough for just parents to do it.

300
00:25:33,448 --> 00:25:35,283
That's probably enough

301
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:39,120
Erika is my wife

302
00:25:41,873 --> 00:25:43,124
I know

303
00:25:44,084 --> 00:25:46,378
A special seat that everyone envy

304
00:25:47,379 --> 00:25:49,506
you were finally happy

305
00:25:52,342 --> 00:25:53,510
happy

306
00:26:13,238 --> 00:26:17,450
(Yukiya) The question is who to use and how?

307
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:25,041
By showing off Seiichiro Ise's kindness⸺

308
00:26:26,084 --> 00:26:27,877
Kyoko Ise...

309
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:36,970
erase from that house

310
00:27:06,833 --> 00:27:11,838
(humming)

311
00:27:18,345 --> 00:27:20,055
(Erika) That's wonderful.

312
00:27:20,138 --> 00:27:22,307
Ah... what? suddenly

313
00:27:22,390 --> 00:27:25,602
(Erika) I'm sorry, I heard your happy voice.

314
00:27:26,478 --> 00:27:27,354
(Kyoko) Hey

315
00:27:28,021 --> 00:27:32,192
Which do you think is better, this one or this one?

316
00:27:33,443 --> 00:27:36,196
I think both would suit your mother-in-law⸺

317
00:27:36,279 --> 00:27:39,532
The silhouette of this outfit is wonderful.

318
00:27:39,616 --> 00:27:41,868
Gray is this year's trend⸺

319
00:27:41,951 --> 00:27:45,413
I think this is a good option if you are dining with young people.

320
00:27:45,497 --> 00:27:49,167
Well then, I guess I'll do what the president says.

321
00:27:49,250 --> 00:27:51,378
Hehe... I'm sorry.

322
00:27:52,212 --> 00:27:54,673
copper? Start working

323
00:27:54,756 --> 00:27:56,466
Not at all yet

324
00:27:56,549 --> 00:27:59,219
Ah, Seiichiro-san said that.

325
00:27:59,302 --> 00:28:02,013
I'm glad I had you as my president.

326
00:28:03,264 --> 00:28:05,892
Well, now⸺

327
00:28:05,975 --> 00:28:09,062
You are the most convenient

328
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:12,732
Well, please do your best.

329
00:28:12,816 --> 00:28:13,775
yes

330
00:28:21,866 --> 00:28:22,867
Mother-in-law

331
00:28:24,911 --> 00:28:27,872
I have to ask you something I don't understand, but...

332
00:28:27,956 --> 00:28:32,168
Are the people you have been in contact with recently in danger?

333
00:28:32,919 --> 00:28:34,462
(Kyoko) What?

334
00:28:34,546 --> 00:28:39,175
Ever since Satoshi-san happened, I've been curious about what people think of me.

335
00:28:39,259 --> 00:28:40,593
Father-in-law too⸺

336
00:28:40,677 --> 00:28:43,972
Be careful of new people approaching you.

337
00:28:44,472 --> 00:28:46,850
What are you saying strangely?

338
00:28:46,933 --> 00:28:48,268
Satoshi-kun⸺

339
00:28:48,351 --> 00:28:50,854
Is it because someone held a grudge against you?

340
00:28:50,937 --> 00:28:53,898
It's wrong to do things that cause people to hold grudges against you.

341
00:28:53,982 --> 00:28:55,316
Seeds I sowed myself

342
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:57,819
I feel sorry for you, but I can't help it.

343
00:28:58,611 --> 00:29:00,029
I agree

344
00:29:00,905 --> 00:29:02,866
(Kyoko) It's SNS now!

345
00:29:02,949 --> 00:29:07,036
People who say things like that about the Ise family are just lazy people.

346
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:09,330
Former idol or something⸺

347
00:29:09,414 --> 00:29:13,293
If you have an affair, they'll jump on you right away.

348
00:29:18,548 --> 00:29:19,632
surely

349
00:29:58,630 --> 00:29:59,756
(sound of door closing)

350
00:31:20,128 --> 00:31:21,629
checkmate

351
00:31:22,714 --> 00:31:23,798
Ah...

352
00:31:25,133 --> 00:31:27,594
your hands are too gentle

353
00:31:28,428 --> 00:31:31,389
You need to confuse me more

354
00:31:31,890 --> 00:31:33,892
Kyoko-san, you are strong.

355
00:31:35,602 --> 00:31:39,147
You can't play chess with a kind heart.

356
00:31:40,356 --> 00:31:42,817
There's a French proverb.

357
00:31:44,694 --> 00:31:48,114
You have to challenge your opponent with the intention of defeating their ego⸺

358
00:31:48,197 --> 00:31:51,576
I'm going to lose, King of Marble

359
00:31:53,453 --> 00:31:54,579
Hehe...

360
00:32:01,586 --> 00:32:02,712
(Girl) Yukini Curry is delicious.

361
00:32:02,795 --> 00:32:05,465
delicious? Good, eat a lot

362
00:32:05,548 --> 00:32:06,382
(Girl) Yeah

363
00:32:06,966 --> 00:32:08,176
- (Yukiya) Yes - (Boy) Thank you.

364
00:32:08,259 --> 00:32:09,218
(Yukiya) Yes.

365
00:32:10,219 --> 00:32:11,763
Everything else is fine

366
00:32:15,516 --> 00:32:16,893
Ah...

367
00:32:18,436 --> 00:32:19,979
(Juna) I'm sorry.

368
00:32:20,063 --> 00:32:22,482
It's okay, it will come off if you wash it.

369
00:32:23,232 --> 00:32:24,609
Before this

370
00:32:26,194 --> 00:32:27,695
We met again

371
00:32:30,448 --> 00:32:31,532
what happened?

372
00:32:32,033 --> 00:32:33,618
(Kotoko) I'm sorry.

373
00:32:34,911 --> 00:32:36,371
nice smell

374
00:32:36,454 --> 00:32:37,288
Ahhh...

375
00:32:37,789 --> 00:32:40,917
If you haven't had dinner yet, please stop by.

376
00:32:43,836 --> 00:32:45,213
but…

377
00:32:46,756 --> 00:32:48,049
that…

378
00:32:50,843 --> 00:32:53,221
I don't have any on hand right now

379
00:32:56,099 --> 00:32:57,642
Hey, let's go home.

380
00:32:57,725 --> 00:33:02,021
I don't like it! I don't want to eat dinner alone

381
00:33:02,105 --> 00:33:04,899
- (Kotoko) Kina-chan - (Yukiya) Um... mother

382
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:08,111
If that's the case, don't worry about it

383
00:33:08,194 --> 00:33:12,323
Rather, our house is for such times.

384
00:33:42,687 --> 00:33:45,148
(Sano) Understood. Excuse me.

385
00:33:50,570 --> 00:33:55,700
(mobile phone vibrator)

386
00:33:56,451 --> 00:33:57,452
hello

387
00:33:57,535 --> 00:34:00,413
(Masayuki) Ah, sorry, sorry, are you still at the company?

388
00:34:00,997 --> 00:34:04,417
Yeah, I don't think I'll be that late today.

389
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:08,546
(Masayuki) That's fine, but isn't there a fountain pen in the president's office?

390
00:34:08,629 --> 00:34:10,006
Wannian pen?

391
00:34:10,089 --> 00:34:13,176
(Masayuki) Yeah, I borrowed it from my dad⸺

392
00:34:13,259 --> 00:34:15,845
I feel like I lent it to someone

393
00:34:15,928 --> 00:34:18,222
I think it was Satoshi-kun.

394
00:34:18,306 --> 00:34:20,892
He's so sloppy when it comes to that kind of thing.

395
00:34:21,350 --> 00:34:26,481
Ah, is this it? Golden wood grain...

396
00:34:26,564 --> 00:34:28,274
(Masayuki) Oh yeah, yeah!

397
00:34:28,357 --> 00:34:30,193
It's a long-established German brand⸺

398
00:34:30,276 --> 00:34:34,363
My dad liked it so much that he would kill me if I lost it.

399
00:34:34,447 --> 00:34:37,492
It was dangerous, thank me.

400
00:34:37,575 --> 00:34:39,494
(Masayuki) Thank you, that was helpful.

401
00:34:40,536 --> 00:34:43,331
Well then, should I leave it on your father-in-law's desk?

402
00:34:43,414 --> 00:34:45,374
(Masayuki) Yeah, nice to meet you.

403
00:34:45,458 --> 00:34:46,667
Yes

404
00:35:32,296 --> 00:35:33,965
(Fuyu) Welcome back

405
00:35:34,048 --> 00:35:37,176
Ah... I'm tired

406
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:41,264
(Fuyu) Thank you for your hard work. Would you like to have dinner soon?

407
00:35:41,347 --> 00:35:44,058
Yeah, what about your mother-in-law and Miyabi?

408
00:35:44,141 --> 00:35:46,060
(Fuyu) Now we are taking a bath together⸺

409
00:35:46,143 --> 00:35:47,186
I think it's just right

410
00:35:47,270 --> 00:35:48,729
Also?

411
00:35:48,813 --> 00:35:50,898
That's what happens when I'm not around⸺

412
00:35:50,982 --> 00:35:52,942
It's like I'm not doing anything

413
00:35:54,443 --> 00:35:56,821
(Fuyu) I will prepare dinner.

414
00:35:57,822 --> 00:35:58,990
Huh...

415
00:36:21,095 --> 00:36:23,097
♪～

416
00:36:28,019 --> 00:36:29,478
(Yukiya) Is it gone?

417
00:36:29,562 --> 00:36:31,689
(fuyu) I'm sorry.

418
00:36:32,315 --> 00:36:36,694
I did put it together with my husband's mail⸺

419
00:36:36,777 --> 00:36:41,490
There was no news this morning, so I went to check just in case.

420
00:36:42,575 --> 00:36:45,870
It seems like you haven't seen your mail yet.

421
00:36:46,537 --> 00:36:50,791
No matter how hard I searched, I couldn't find that envelope.

422
00:37:00,134 --> 00:37:02,345
-(Sano) I brought you here-(Erika) Yeah.

423
00:37:04,639 --> 00:37:09,185
Ah... My name is Satake from Marble and you contacted me.

424
00:37:09,268 --> 00:37:11,437
(Erika) Welcome.

425
00:37:20,488 --> 00:37:21,656
(Yukiya) I will contact you again.

426
00:37:45,388 --> 00:37:46,889
(Reo) I will not sell Kyoko.

427
00:37:46,973 --> 00:37:49,016
(Yukiya) I was treated really well, so

428
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:51,394
-(Reo) Thanks to Erika-san-(Kyoko) You don't have a good eye for people.

429
00:37:51,477 --> 00:37:52,979
(Masayuki) Even though I'm celebrating my mother's birthday.

430
00:37:53,062 --> 00:37:55,898
(Kyoko) Isn't it the best entertainment?

431
00:37:55,982 --> 00:37:57,400
(Erika) I'll handle it myself.

432
00:37:57,483 --> 00:37:58,484
Look aside

433
00:37:58,567 --> 00:38:01,570
(Reo) I want to get serious about this business.

434
00:38:02,113 --> 00:38:03,572
(Yukiya) Keeping my mother in a good mood⸺

435
00:38:03,656 --> 00:38:06,742
It's important to Marble, isn't it?

436
00:38:06,826 --> 00:38:10,204
Mom, it's been a long time

437
00:38:11,372 --> 00:38:12,456
I am⸺

438
00:38:13,124 --> 00:38:16,127
I'll never forgive you

439
00:38:17,586 --> 00:38:22,049
I will destroy every single one of you.

440
00:38:23,843 --> 00:38:25,845
～♪
